author: NPR Music
description:
The 2025 Tiny Desk Contest closed 2 weeks ago with a record number of entries. While our judges review the thousands (!) we received, we'll be sharing some standouts here. Discover new artists to love by following along with our #DeskOfTheDay features.

Our first #DeskOfTheDay is "The Weekend" by  @WestHillRoad  from Stamford, Conn.!

Watch the full video here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b_BwYhtCSJI
title: #DeskOfTheDay: "The Weekend" by West Hill Road
